title: DAKINE Tanner Hall Fillmore Mitt
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2012 Tanner Hall Fillmore Mitt:

- Insert: Hipora® waterproof
- Insulation: High loft synthetic [ 60g / 170g ]

- Lining: 230g mid-weight fleece

- Nose wipe thumb panels
